snippet.textDisplay:
Ok so can I just say what I think, and what I’m going to do.
I have loved DanPlan for ages, and I see them as my idol. Their creativity has inspired me, making me do my own art and such.
And that won’t change.
Im upset that Stephen (understandably) left DanPlan - I know it won’t be the same without him, his humour always made me laugh even when I was in my darkest moods. But I am staying subscribed to DanPlan.
I still love the DanPlan team, and I don’t think that their subscribers should quit just because we are upset about this. This is their money, their love and their creativity in a channel (though Dan unfortunately may not see it as that anymore) and we should never ruin their own joy because of it. DanPlan, if your reading, I will keep watching your videos, and I will stay subscribed. I have also subscribed to Stephen, and all I can do now is wish luck for them both.
